resources.string:
I am a highly motivated software developer with two years of experience in the field. 

My project portfolio includes work in C# and Java, and I have a fundamental understanding of machine learning. 

Seeking new challenges, I embarked on the NUS-ISS GDipSA program, where I adeptly mastered Agile Methodology and SDLC for application design. 

During my internship at NUS-DCEE as part of the GDipSA program, I functioned as a full-stack developer. I utilized Next.js for the frontend, NodeJS for the backend, and AWS for cloud services. 

Additionally, I was involved in creating 3D structural designs for buildings. 

As an enthusiastic and proactive learner with a genuine passion for coding and problem-solving, I am now actively seeking opportunities to apply my skills, enthusiasm, and strong work ethic in a software development role. 

 I had done a lot of projects implemented with Java, C#, Android, Ruby-On-Rails, ReactJs, NextJs, NodeJs, AWS, MySQL, MongoDB, PostgreSQL.
